test_large_range:
assert [8, 9, 10] == [9]
  At index 0 diff: 8 != 9
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 9
  Full diff:
  - [9]
  + [8, 9, 10]
test_even_range:
assert [16, 18, 20] == [18]
  At index 0 diff: 16 != 18
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 18
  Full diff:
  - [18]
  + [16, 18, 20]
